<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.1.5">
<l>aṭittalamun tāmaraiyē yaṅkaiyum paṅkayamē yeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>muṭittalamum poṟpūṇu meṉneñcat tuḷḷakalā veṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>vaṭittaṭaṅkaṇ malaravaḷō varaiyākat tuḷḷiruppā ḷeṉkiṉ ṟāḷāl</l>
<l>kaṭikkamalam kaḷḷukukkum kaṇṇapurat tammāṉaik kaṇṭāḷ kollō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The soles of his feet are lotuses; his lovely hands are lotuses, too,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“His crown placement and gold jewels never leave from within my heart,”</l>
<l rend="indent">she declares;</l>
<l>“Is she of the blossom with wide sharp eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who is on his mountain[-like] chest?” she declares.</l>
<l>Did she see the lord of Kaṇṇapuram where nectar drips from fragrant lotuses?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
